settings.description: Honestly loosely based on one level from the SMBX game 'the invasion 2', for remember a level with the hammer bros themes and mario bros elements? well... here I'm trying to go for that theme!
I was doing good at first but I gave up...

A remake of an unused level hidden in SMB3 NES/All-Stars SNES ROM.
I wanted to use Wrap Around but I gave up because many objects didn't go in intended positions.
Wendy gets her Airship redesigned, With various Airships added for assistant, Mario goes to the airship by using an mini airship instead of climbing, Good Luck Defeating Wendy & Finding a Secret Exit
Mario goes to the fridge to get a glass of milk
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the bunker part; you will see this again soon.
